## üöÄ Getting Started

New to R or geological data analysis? Start with these foundational posts:

1. **[Setting up R for Geological Work](/posts/r-setup-geology)** - Essential packages and workflows
2. **[Your First Drillhole Analysis](/posts/first-drillhole-analysis)** - Basic data loading and visualization  
3. **[Introduction to Geostatistics in R](/posts/geostatistics-intro)** - Variogram modeling basics
4. **[Creating Geological Maps](/posts/geological-mapping)** - Spatial visualization techniques

